---
title: Easy Teriyaki-Glazed Beef Burger with Creamy Slaw & Sesame Fries
description: We're revamping burger night by giving juicy beef patties a teriyaki glaze, and sprinkling potato fries with sesame seeds to jazz up their flavour. A rainbow slaw with coconut sweet chilli mayo takes the salad portion of the meal to new heights too.
